Name: Nottavan Para View Point
Desciption: "The Unexplored Trail in Chengannur. People who loves Quite and Isolated places away from the hush and gush of Cities should definately visit the place."

Name: Krishnapuram Palace
Desciption: "The Krishnapuram Palace is a palace and museum located in Haripad near Alappuzha in Alappuzha district"

Name: Azheekal Beach
Desciption: "Azheekal Beach is an 800 meter long beach on the coast of the Arabian Sea, in Karunagappally Taluk of Kollam Metropolitan Area, Kerala, India. The beach got this name from the Malayalam word Aazhee, which means confluence of backwaters and the Sea."
